metadata.name: The Seat of The Gods
metadata.description:
The Gods gather in the palace of Zeus on Mount Olympus to share discourse over the ongoing war below. Each one carries with them a secret.

><><><><><><><><

“The Seat of The Gods” is a digitally illustrated and animated OE, in the Secrets OE collection. Artworks in this collection are glimpses into the wider narrative in the world of Secrets. They are collectibles that relate to the upcoming comic book series.
